description: Do not add UI or unit tests for Compose Preview-only helpers
alwaysApply: true
---

# Compose Preview helpers — no tests

- **Do not** add **UI tests** (Compose UI tests, Robolectric `runComposeUiTest`, etc.) for types that exist **only** to support **Compose tooling previews**.
- **Do not** add dedicated `*Test.kt` classes whose only purpose is to verify **preview sample data** or **`PreviewParameterProvider.values`** sequences.
- Examples of out-of-scope subjects: `PreviewParameterProvider` implementations, preview-only data classes used with `@PreviewParameter`, and similar **non-`@Composable`** preview wiring.

Rely on **`@Preview`** in source and IDE preview for these; test **`@Composable`** UI and real behavior in the components/screens that use them.
